@node general "General Information"
@prev MAIN
@next install

Back in the old days (when 48K of RAM was a lot of memory) there was a game for the Apple ][ called "DogFight".  One of the simplest games I know, it was also possibly the most fun, due to it's amost unique ability to allow up to 7 people to simultaneously play.

I'm not going to claim that this program is DogFight reincarnate.  However, DogFight! does share some similarities with the "original" game.  Anyone who remembers the old DogFight will notice that several features are missing in this version; look for future releases of DogFight! for improvements.  In addition, DogFight! contains some options the original doesn't.

@endnode

